headline: Cigna Group (CI) Announces US$1.51 Per Share Cash Dividend for September 2025
summary: The Cigna Group (CI) recently declared a dividend of $1.51 per share, reaffirming its dedication to providing shareholder value. Despite this positive development, the company's share price remained flat over the last week, contrasting with a broader market upswing of 1.3%. The declaration, while beneficial, seemed insufficient to overcome the prevailing market momentum fueled by trade deal optimism and anticipated tech earnings, which drove major indices to record highs.
